Hi Rostyslav,
I'm sorry to hear that your ads have been in moderation for more than a week. The ad approval process usually takes between 1-2 business days. Sometimes it can take a bit longer, but a week is definitely unusual.
I recommend checking if there are any issues with your ad content that might be causing the delay. You can also reach out to our support team for further assistance.
Here's an article that might help you: [How to create your first ad](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/17618196971149-How-to-create-your-first-ad).
If you need further assistance, please let me know!
